Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.95,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克?真是的，到哪去了嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.06,0:00:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好可愛，小松鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!妮絲!救命啊!妮絲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.10,0:00:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…可惡，盡遇上倒楣事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.57,0:00:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼會有個陷阱在這啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.94,0:00:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是本人我所計畫好才挖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.01,0:00:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少得意!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.72,0:00:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想掉進來呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是你來搶這封信的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把龍媽媽的信還來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.26,0:00:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要還你啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.18,0:00:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.86,0:00:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面龍媽媽一定有寫\N有關餅乾的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.42,0:00:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 還來!\N- 不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.54,0:01:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是龍的語言…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.97,0:01:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本看不懂啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.98,0:01:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行，爬不上去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.65,0:01:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若是騎士的話就想點辦法!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.15,0:01:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少在亂講…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是能咻的一聲就飛上去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.39,0:01:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我怎樣都沒想到呢?謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走一步了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.57,0:01:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.17,0:01:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了，龍寶寶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.31,0:01:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，信上到底寫了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.05,0:01:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多加小心，就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.18,0:01:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，哈哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.88,0:01:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，我好像忘了什麼了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.15,0:01:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會就此罷休的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要吃到瑪法的餅乾!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.23,0:01:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看哦
